headline: Wind-Related Stocks Hit by Trump Construction Halt
summary: The Trump administration on Monday halted the construction of all U.S. offshore wind projects, a sweeping move aimed at hobbling one of the president’s least favorite industries.  Shares in Danish energy company Orsted, which is leading two of the projects, fell more than 12% on the news.  Dominion Energy, the lead developer on another project, fell more than 5% and was the worst performer in the S&P 500.

content.title: Wind-Related Stocks Hit by Trump Construction Halt
content.summary: The Trump administration on Monday halted the construction of all U.S. offshore wind projects, a sweeping move aimed at hobbling one of the president’s least favorite industries.  Shares in Danish energy company Orsted, which is leading two of the projects, fell more than 12% on the news.  Dominion Energy, the lead developer on another project, fell more than 5% and was the worst performer in the S&P 500.
